name: Ionic Arizona Meetup
body:
### Welcome to the Ionic Az Meetup.

We meet monthly in the Phoenix Arizona area typically on the last Tuesday of the month.  

View the scheduled meetings at [http://meetup.com/ionic-az](http://meetup.com/ionic-az)

### Contact

You can contact us on the meetup page or at organizers@ ionic-az.org
